00249 void FusionCELDataCalvinTest::CompareHeaderData()
00250 {
00251         // Check all header values
00252         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetVersion() == calvinCel->GetVersion());
00253         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetCols() == calvinCel->GetCols());
00254         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetRows() == calvinCel->GetRows());
00255         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetNumCells() == calvinCel->GetNumCells());
00256 
00257         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetHeader() == L"");
00258         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetAlg() == calvinCel->GetAlgorithmName());
00259         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetChipType() == calvinCel->GetArrayType());
00260 
00261         ParameterNameValueTypeVector algParams;
00262         calvinCel->GetAlgorithmParameters(algParams);
00263 
00264         // Test GetParams and GetAlgorithmParameters
00265         std::wstring calvinParamString;
00266         for (ParameterNameValueTypeIt ci = algParams.begin(); ci != algParams.end(); ++ci)
00267         {
00268                 // This is a repeat of the calvin adapter implementation, oh well, a file change will not break it
00269                 if (algParams.begin() != ci)
00270                         calvinParamString += L";";
00271                 calvinParamString += ci->GetName();
00272                 calvinParamString += L":";
00273                 calvinParamString += ci->ToString();
00274         }
00275         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinParamString == fusionCel->GetParams());
00276         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinParamString == fusionCel->GetAlgorithmParameters());
00277 
00278         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetNumberAlgorithmParameters() == (int)algParams.size());
00279         int paramCount = fusionCel->GetNumberAlgorithmParameters();
00280         ParameterNameValueTypeIt ci = algParams.begin();
00281         for (int ip = 0; ip < paramCount && ci != algParams.end(); ++ip, ++ci)
00282         {
00283                 wstring fusionParamTag = fusionCel->GetAlgorithmParameterTag(ip);
00284                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ci->GetName() == fusionParamTag);
00285                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ci->ToString() == fusionCel->GetAlgorithmParameter(fusionParamTag.c_str()));
00286         }
00287 
00288         // Test GetParameters
00289         FusionTagValuePairTypeList& fusionList = fusionCel->GetParameters();
00290         std::list<FusionTagValuePairType>::iterator fi = fusionList.begin();
00291 
00292         int32_t pi = 0;
00293         int32_t algParamCnt = (int32_t)algParams.size();
00294 
00295         for (; fi != fusionList.end() && pi < algParamCnt; ++fi, ++pi)
00296         {
00297                 std::wstring t1 = fi->Tag;
00298                 std::wstring v1 = fi->Value;
00299                 std::wstring t2 = algParams.at(pi).GetName();
00300                 std::wstring v2 = algParams.at(pi).ToString();
00301                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fi->Tag == algParams.at(pi).GetName());
00302                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fi->Value == algParams.at(pi).ToString());
00303                 if (fi->DetailedType().GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::FloatType)
00304                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fi->DetailedType().GetValueFloat() == algParams.at(pi).GetValueFloat());
00305                 else if (fi->DetailedType().GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::Int32Type)
00306                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fi->DetailedType().GetValueInt32() == algParams.at(pi).GetValueInt32());
00307         }
00308 
00309         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetCellMargin() == 2);
00310 
00311         XYCoordVector outlierCoords;
00312         calvinCel->GetOutlierCoords(outlierCoords);
00313         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetNumOutliers() == (int)outlierCoords.size());
00314 
00315         XYCoordVector maskCoords;
00316         calvinCel->GetMaskedCoords(maskCoords);
00317         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetNumMasked() == (int)maskCoords.size());
00318 
00319         CompareGrids();
00320 }

00322 void FusionCELDataCalvinTest::ComparePartialDatHeaders()
00323 {
00324         // Find the parent DAT
00325         GenDataHdrVectorIt begin, end; 
00326         calvinCel->GetFileHeader()->GetGenericDataHdr()->GetParentIterators(begin, end);
00327         std::wstring datHeader;
00328         u_int16_t maxPixel = 0, minPixel = 0;
00329 
00330         for (GenDataHdrVectorIt ii = begin; ii != end; ++ii)
00331         {
00332                 if (ii->GetFileTypeId() == SCAN_ACQUISITION_DATA_TYPE)
00333                 {
00334                         // found the right header, now look for the parameter
00335                         ParameterNameValueType nvt;
00336                         if (ii->FindNameValParam(DAT_HEADER_PARAM_NAME, nvt))
00337                         {
00338                                 datHeader = nvt.GetValueText();
00339                         }
00340                         if (ii->FindNameValParam(MAX_PIXEL_INTENSITY_PARAM_NAME, nvt))
00341                         {
00342                                 if (nvt.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::UInt16Type)
00343                                         maxPixel = nvt.GetValueUInt16();
00344                         }
00345 
00346                         if (ii->FindNameValParam(MIN_PIXEL_INTENSITY_PARAM_NAME, nvt))
00347                         {
00348                                 if (nvt.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::UInt16Type)
00349                                         minPixel = nvt.GetValueUInt16();
00350                         }
00351                 }
00352         }
00353 
00354         u_int32_t expectedMax = 0, expectedMin = 0;     // Needs to be a 4 byte int to keep swscanf from messing up the stack frame.
00355         std::wstring fusionDatHeader = fusionCel->GetDatHeader();
00356         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionDatHeader.find(datHeader, 0) != wstring::npos);
00357         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(swscanf(fusionDatHeader.c_str(), L"[%d..%d]", &expectedMin, &expectedMax) == 2);
00358         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(minPixel == expectedMin);
00359         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(maxPixel == expectedMax);
00360 
00361 }

00363 void FusionCELDataCalvinTest::CompareGrids()
00364 {
00365         affymetrix_fusion_io::FGridCoords fusionGrid = fusionCel->GetGridCorners();
00366 
00367         ParameterNameValueType nvt;
00368         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinCel->FindAlgorithmParameter(GRIDULX_PARAM_NAME, nvt));
00369         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvt.GetValueFloat() == fusionGrid.upperleft.x);
00370         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinCel->FindAlgorithmParameter(GRIDULY_PARAM_NAME, nvt));
00371         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvt.GetValueFloat() == fusionGrid.upperleft.y);
00372 
00373         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinCel->FindAlgorithmParameter(GRIDURX_PARAM_NAME, nvt));
00374         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvt.GetValueFloat() == fusionGrid.upperright.x);
00375         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinCel->FindAlgorithmParameter(GRIDURY_PARAM_NAME, nvt));
00376         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvt.GetValueFloat() == fusionGrid.upperright.y);
00377 
00378         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinCel->FindAlgorithmParameter(GRIDLRX_PARAM_NAME, nvt));
00379         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvt.GetValueFloat() == fusionGrid.lowerright.x);
00380         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinCel->FindAlgorithmParameter(GRIDLRY_PARAM_NAME, nvt));
00381         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvt.GetValueFloat() == fusionGrid.lowerright.y);
00382 
00383         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinCel->FindAlgorithmParameter(GRIDLLX_PARAM_NAME, nvt));
00384         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvt.GetValueFloat() == fusionGrid.lowerleft.x);
00385         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinCel->FindAlgorithmParameter(GRIDLLY_PARAM_NAME, nvt));
00386         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvt.GetValueFloat() == fusionGrid.lowerleft.y);
